imator","company":"Imported from resume CSV","description":"Position : Quantity Surveyor | Period : | 2023-2024 | Project : Dubai South Project | 300,000 AED ROLES AND RESPONSIBILITIES ➢ Prepared and filed Interim Payment Applications (IPA) for correct billing. ➢ Oversaw Material on Site (MOS) reports while working with vendors. ➢ Work Inspection Requests (WIR) that have been verified for quality and contractual requirements. ➢ Tracked project development, coordinating IPA submissions with the conclusion of on-site work. ➢ Worked in tandem with the site team to ensure correct reporting of materials and work progress. ➢ Completing project cost final accounting. ➢ Helping with forecasting and cost report development. ➢ Notifying interested parties of financial condition. ARCO TURNKEY SOLUTIONS CONTRACTING LLC. || Position : Quantity Surveyor | Period : | 2021-2023 | Project : Al Forsan City Mall Abu Dhabi | Value: 2.7 Million AED ROLES AND RESPONSIBILITIES Pre contract ➢ Gathering Bills of Quantities, procurement schedules, and tender papers. ➢ Creating thorough project budgets and cost projections ➢ valuated and compared subcontractor and supplier tender quotations for cost efficiency. ➢ Assisting in bid preparations for competitive tenders Post contract ➢ Measured the location and confirmed the quantities to ensure proper invoicing. ➢ Examining and drafting orders for variations. ➢ Contribution to final accounts preparation. ➢ Frequent site inspections to confirm the status of the work and the financial effects of delays or scope modifications. NAWALOKA CONSTRUCTION COMPANY. || Position : Quantity Surveyor | Period : | 2018-2021 | Project : Residential Apartments, Shopping Malls, Villas ROLES AND RESPONSIBILITIES ➢ Prepared detailed Bills of Quantities (BOQ) and tender documentation in alignment with project specifications. ➢ Review, evaluate, finalize and settle subcontractor’s payments. ➢ Compiling final accounts, payment applications, and interim appraisals. ➢ Keeping thorough records of all financial transactions related to the project ➢ Assisting the senior quantity surveyor with change order administration, job progress verification, and site inspections. ➢ Comparing Quotations, and ordering materials with the approval of the Tendering & Procurement Director. ➢ Conducted quantity take-offs and material take-offs for civil and MEP works. ➢ Assisted in the procurement process, including RFQ preparation, evaluating supplier quotes, and preparing purchase orders. ➢ Supported in preparing and issuing tender documents to subcontractors and suppliers."}]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, 'F:\Resume All 1\Resume PDF\Nafly Resume (1).pdf', 'Name: Nafly Ahamed Nisham

