ions related to the project ➢ Assisting the senior quantity surveyor with change order administration, job progress verification, and site inspections. ➢ Comparing Quotations, and ordering materials with the approval of the Tendering & Procurement Director. ➢ Conducted quantity take-offs and material take-offs for civil and MEP works. ➢ Assisted in the procurement process, including RFQ preparation, evaluating supplier quotes, and preparing purchase orders. ➢ Supported in preparing and issuing tender documents to subcontractors and suppliers.

